        <div class="fbg-row lmRow ui-sortable" data-lm-customclass=""><div data-lm-columnwidth="12" class="fbg-col-xs-12 column lmColumn ui-sortable" data-lm-customclass=""><div class="ge-content ge-content-type-gridHTML ui-droppable" data-ge-content-type="gridHTML"><div class="fbg-container-fluid lmLayoutComponent" data-lm-id="lm337" data-lm-componenttype="StandardOneColumn" data-lm-componenttitle=""><div class="fbg-row"><div class="fbg-col-xs-12"><div class="iCreateDynaToken" data-lm-tokenid="StandardOneColumnTK1" data-icrt-tk-cfg="StandardColumnContent" id="StandardOneColumnTK1_lm1"><p>Council is the main governing and legislative body for the City of St. John's. It consists of the Mayor, Deputy Mayor, five ward councillors and 4 councillors-at-large.</p>
<p><a class="defaultButton-Primary" title="Open new window to view Find Your Ward" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://apps.stjohns.ca/wardlookup/WardLookup.aspx" target="_blank" aria-label="Find Your Ward opens in new window">Find Your Ward</a></p>
