</ul>
<h2>Meetings and agendas</h2>
<p>St. Johns City Council conducts the business of the City through a regular public meeting, held every second Tuesday at 3 p.m., alternating with <a title="View our Council Meetings  page" href="/en/city-hall/council-meetings.aspx?_mid_=10965">Committee of the Whole</a>.&nbsp;Regular Council Meetings are&nbsp;<a title="Open new window to view live streamed" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://apps.stjohns.ca/escribe/Escribe.aspx" target="_blank" aria-label="live streamed opens in new window">live streamed</a>&nbsp;via our website, and the video, minutes and agendas of past meetings are accessible by selecting the date for the meeting you would like to view.</p>
<p><a class="defaultButton-Primary" title="Open new window to view See the Council calendar, agendas and minutes" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://apps.stjohns.ca/escribe/Escribe.aspx" target="_blank" aria-label="See the Council calendar, agendas and minutes opens in new window">See the Council calendar, agendas and minutes</a></p>
